#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn38.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn38.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Dhammavādīpañhāsutta "
msgstr "3. Principled Speech "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.253, sc1
msgctxt "sn38.3:1.1"
msgid "“Ke nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, loke dhammavādino, ke loke suppaṭipannā, ke loke sugatā”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, who in the world have principled speech? Who in the world practice well? Who are the Holy Ones in the world?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:1.2"
msgid "“Ye kho, āvuso, rāgappahānāya dhammaṃ desenti, dosappahānāya dhammaṃ desenti, mohappahānāya dhammaṃ desenti, te loke dhammavādino. "
msgstr "“Reverend, those who teach principles for giving up greed, hate, and delusion have principled speech in the world. "

msgctxt "sn38.3:1.3"
msgid "Ye kho, āvuso, rāgassa pahānāya paṭipannā, dosassa pahānāya paṭipannā, mohassa pahānāya paṭipannā, te loke suppaṭipannā. "
msgstr "Those who practice for giving up greed, hate, and delusion are practicing well in the world. "

msgctxt "sn38.3:1.4"
msgid "Yesaṃ kho, āvuso, rāgo pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo, doso pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo, moho pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo, te loke sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "Those who have given up greed, hate, and delusion—so they’re cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future—are Holy Ones in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.1"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.3"
msgid "“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti? "
msgstr "“Well, what is it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.4"
msgid "“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāya, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn38.3:2.5"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn38.3:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāyā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the path, this is the practice for giving up that greed, hate, and delusion.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.7"
msgid "“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā, etassa rāgassa dosassa mohassa pahānāya. "
msgstr "“This is a fine path, a fine practice, for giving up greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn38.3:2.8"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Just this much is enough to be diligent.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.3:2.9"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

